        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="secondary-buttons">
    </div>
    <p class="note">Requires <a href="https://maniaplanet.com/download">ManiaPlanet</a> installed and owning <b><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/developer/nadeo/list/34687/">all TrackMania 2 games</a> (Canyon, Stadium, Valley, and Lagoon)</b>. <a href="turbo#installation">(installation guide)</a></p>

